{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "中秋月圆决战夜，铁大爷端坐四海楼部署。侏儒朱儒回报：慕容一行已到，唯独缺柳明秋，但有一神秘白袍蒙面女子随行，浑身散发致命诱惑。朱儒分析慕容外表儒雅内里却藏有卑鄙残暴的另一面，且慕容全程坐椅不动，令人费解。慕容率六组人马逼近，铁大爷决定先击第二、三组共十二人。与此同时，在昆仑山深处的白石大屋中，一个穿白棉布长袍的神秘人正在研究楚留香的卷宗，包括'楚留香之死'。有人来报：飞蛾行动已开始。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "情况很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "就好像大老板预料中一样，该来的差不多全都来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "差不多?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "差不多是差多少?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "只差一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "柳明秋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "这个不瞎的瞎子本来一直是个独来独往的人，可是最近却忽然投靠了江南慕容。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "谁也不知道是为了什么，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "更让人想不通的是，他今天居然没有来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "不该来的人来了几个?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "一个用白巾蒙着脸，穿着一件直统统的白布袍，看来仿佛很神秘的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "慕容是坐着一顶小轿来的，这个女人一直都跟在小轿边。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "你怎么知道这个人是个女人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "你非但看不见她的脸，连她的身材都看不见，你怎么能确定她一定是个女人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "因为我第一眼看见她就热了起来，全身上下忽然间就热起来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "她全身上下我全都看不见，可是我那时候的感觉，居然比看见七八十个赤裸裸的漂亮小姑娘还冲动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "她每走一步路，每一个动作，都带着种说不出的诱惑。尤其是她的眼神。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "她的眼睛里就好像有只看不见的手，随时都可以一下子就把你的魂抓走。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "你知不知道这个女人是什么来路?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "可是我知道她一定是慕容的女人，她一直都跟着他，几乎寸步不离。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "这一代的慕容是个什么样的人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "他有些什么特别的地方?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "这就很难说了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "这个慕容，好像跟上几代慕容都不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "表面看来，他也跟别的慕容没什么两样，也是一副自命儒雅，高高在上的样子，脸上也完全没有一点血色，就像是个死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "不是死人，",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "是贵族。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "他们常常说，只有最高贵的人，才会有这种脸色，不但要苍白得全无血色，而且更白得发蓝。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "因为他们这种人，通常都不需要在阳光下流血流汗的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "可是这一代的这一个慕容，却绝不是这种自我陶醉的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "这个慕容外表看起来虽然跟他们一样，可是……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "可是在他这个躯壳下，总好像有另外一个人隐藏在里面。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "一个什么样的人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "一个和他外表完全相反的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "一个又卑鄙，又下流，又阴险，又恶毒，又粗俗，又刁钻，又无耻，又残暴的流氓和骗子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "他的武功呢?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "他的武功怎么样?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我看不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "你怎么会看不出?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "难道你看不见他?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我看得见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "可是我只能看见他这个人，却看不见他的动作和神态。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "因为他根本没有动过，连小指头都没有动过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "而且脸上连一点表情都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "他的脸，就像是用大理石雕出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "他没有动，只因为他一直都坐在一张很舒服的椅子上。一动也没有动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "你是不是说，他是坐在一张椅子上被人抬来的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "他有没有受伤?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "至少我看不出他像受了伤的样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "他的腿当然也没有断!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "他的腿好像还在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "慕容世家好像也不会选一个断了腿的人来掌门户。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "那么这个慕容是怎么回事呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "他既没有受伤，也不是残废，他为什么不自己走路来?为什么不去弄匹马来骑骑?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "这个问题实在问得好极了。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "一个人如果做出了一件他本来不该做的事，如果不是因为他太笨，就是因为他太聪明。而且其中一定有问题。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "这个慕容看来好像并不是个笨蛋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "他绝对不是，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "他也许远比你我想像中还聪明。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "他至少知道坐在椅子上被人抬来是有好处的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "什么好处?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "坐在椅子上不但舒服，而且可能保留体力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我们在这里等他，本来是我们以逸待劳，先占了一点便宜，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ru",
      "speaker_name": "朱儒",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "可是现在我们都在站着，他却坐着，反而变得是他在以逸待劳了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "好，说得好，",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ru",
      "text": "那么现在你为什么还不叫人去弄张椅子坐下来?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "你看他们来了多少人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我看不出有多少人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我只看得出他们有六组人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "一组多少人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "组别不同，人数也不同，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "第一组只有两个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "一个坐在椅子上，一个跟在椅子旁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "第二组呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "第二组就有四个人，三组八个，四组十六，五组三十二。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "第二组四个人我认得出三个，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "三个都是好手!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "可是我看，其中最厉害的一个，大概还是我认不出的那一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "你说的一定是丁先生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "我想大概就是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "人长得又细又长，脑袋却又大又扁，看起来就像是个钉子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "他的名字本来就叫做丁子灵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "丁子灵?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "丁子灵，灵钉子，一钉下去，就要人死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "是的，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我说的就是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "不错，这个钉子是有一点可怕，幸好我既不是木头，也不是墙壁，我怕他个鸟?",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "我只不过觉得有点奇怪而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "奇怪什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "一组两人，二组四人，三组有八，四组十六，五组三十二。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "大爷",
      "listener": "char_si_lu",
      "text": "我算来算去，最多也只有五组，你为何却要说是六组?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "那两个抬轿子的人是不是人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们第一次攻击的对象是他们的第二组和第三组，一共十二个人，一次歼灭。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们约定好的讯号一发，行动就开始。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一次行动，必需在击掌四次之间全部完成。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人类其实是非常愚蠢。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_lu",
      "speaker_name": "丝路先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每个人都不想死，用尽千方百计，也想活下去，可是有时候却又偏偏笨得像飞蛾一样，要去扑火。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    }
  ],
